{"type":"answer","id":81410,"parentType":"question","parentId":11396,"uid":20240,"contents":"可以看看联合国每年幸福指数报告<br>\n联合国发布的这份报告主要排名是依据六个方面，来派列全球156个国家，它们分别是：收入 自由 预期寿命 社会支持 信任和慷慨。前10名的国家有共同的特点：富人和穷人之间差距小 税收高 有社会保障机制 长寿命 低腐败率 政府支持和社区有能力来支持需要帮助的人。<br>\n看看你国和沙特的排名差距吧<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/16221706-3a9a30bfb129aab1?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/554/format/webp\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/16221706-3a9a30bfb129aab1?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/554/format/webp\" alt=\"https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/16221706-3a9a30bfb129aab1?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip|imageView2/2/w/554/format/webp\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2019-11-18","agreeCount":1,"discussionCount":0}